âœ… DIMENSION TABLES (Dimensions)

These describe entities (who, what, when, where).

1. dim_customers

From bronze.customers

customer_id

company_name

contact_name

email

phone

country

created_at

2. dim_products

From bronze.products

product_id

product_name

category

base_price

development_hours

version

3. dim_employees

From bronze.employees

employee_id

full_name

